Summary: Fast Moving Greeen Orb or Disk
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile travelling west on S 272nd street, around 8pm. Witnessed Green orb or Disk travelling west toward ocean. As seen through my windsheild while driving. The green light was not a clearance light from an aircraft having built many at Boeing. The light moved in a straight course and went out of site. only lasted maybe 5 seconds. May have been on local news.
